        img.img-responsive(src="/images/hatch-startup-empty.gif")
        h2 You?
        p Designer (UI/UX)
        a.btn.btn-default(href='mailto:awesome@hatchcommunity.be?subject=I want to be a designer at Hatch Start-up Class') Apply

    footer
      h3 Want to join this team?
      p Hatch is still looking for new talent to join our Start-up class.
      a.btn.btn-default(href='mailto:awesome@hatchcommunity.be?subject=Apply for Start-up Class') Join Hatch Start-up Class

